    13/13 P1/P2 reqs from phase 005's catalogue closed via cli-codex gpt-5.5 high
    fast. New mcp_server/lib/cocoindex/daemon-probe.ts; modifications to
    memory-causal-stats.ts, memory-context.ts, memory-crud-health.ts,
    folder-discovery.ts, intent-classifier.ts, query-router.ts. Four new vitest
    files: intent-classifier-corpus, folder-discovery-threshold,
    cocoindex-daemon-probe, causal-stats-output. Packet-focused suites:
    121/121 PASS. Strict validate: exit 0.
    
