    release(mcp-code-mode): v2.0.0.1: Public release - JS→TS migration + pre-release security audit
    
    v2.0.0.0: Spec Kit Memory JavaScript → TypeScript Migration
    - Complete rewrite: 186+ files converted across 16 spec folders (092-107)
    - 85+ critical bugs fixed, 12 non-functional features restored
    - 3,872 tests passing, 0 TypeScript errors, 0 JS source files
    - 1,589 new tests added (100% module export coverage)
    - Documentation accuracy: 303 fixes across ~45 files
    
    v2.0.0.1: Pre-Release Security Audit
    - 27-agent security sweep across all 9 skills, 18 commands, 8 agents
    - 200+ sensitive content replacements (domains, paths, names)
    - Version alignment fixes (mcp-code-mode, mcp-figma)
    - skill_advisor.py dual-threshold bug fix
    - .gitignore hardened (*.sqlite3, *.db, *.cert, __pycache__/)
    - Build documentation added for first-time users
    - Dead links fixed, stale references corrected across 40+ files

